": "عَرَّضَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[q. v.]: (Msb, El-Munáwee: the latter in explaining a trad., q. v. infrà:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taworiyapN", "text_ar": "تَوْرِيَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[signifying as above; or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pretending one thing and meaning another;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "using a word, an expression,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a phrase, which has an obvious meaning, and intending thereby another meaning to which it applies but which is contrary to the obvious one"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; the original meaning of which is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "concealment:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "language whereof one part resembles another in the meanings:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, TA: [in the TA immediately follows the exemplification cited above, from the Msb; whence it seems that this explanation is itself somewhat of a"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mErAD", "text_ar": "معراض"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning what it does not clearly express:]) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlmaEaAriyDu fiY AlkalaAmi", "text_ar": "المَعَارِيضُ فِى الكَلَامِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[thus, with the pl. form, in two copies of the S, and in the TA,] signifies"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alt~aworiyapu biAl$~aYo'i Eani Al$~aYo'i", "text_ar": "التَّوْرِيَةُ بِالشَّىْءِ عَنِ الشَّىْءِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pretending,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "making believe, a thing instead of another thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (S:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maEaAriDu AlkalaAmi", "text_ar": "مَعَارِضُ الكَلَامِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aEoraADuhu", "text_ar": "اَعْرَاضُهُ", "ort